{"tid":1385532,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"呢場運動。經濟先係籌碼，良心唔係。","createTime":"2019-07-30T05:59:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T04:06:42.000Z","uid":280341,"like":97,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"4c718f2fee6af95f1f8cdbaf588ffb0477f4937f","tid":1385532,"uid":280341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:59:21.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">同差佬面對面打再多場，都係輸。他打係「合法」，我地打係違法。甚至打撚死一個警察，佢地可能會驚，但我地會輸得更加多，被拉更多有勇氣嘅年輕人。<br />\n<br />\n如果你地目地係想制造輿論，想政府良心發現，想更加多人企出來，佢地已經證明左俾我地睇。無可能！！任何人都只會係「事不關己，已不勞心。」<br />\n<br />\n要贏，就要做直接對政府有威脋嘅野。<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">經濟先係籌碼，良心唔係。</span></span></strong><br />\n而家全世界都攬警察，但警察太多豬隊友，最驚係被人查佢地所有證據確鑿的惡行。要找突破口，就要先搞警察，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中主力成立獨立調查委員會係第一步。要首先突破政府防線。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n階段性目標，至少要贏一次，社會先會有人企係我地呢邊，先有希望。<br />\n我地好多都草根階層，我地只可以用我地嘅方法，做我地力所能及嘅野。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"82852facb588a03cceca8a79a277b6fcbd8a379d","tid":1385532,"uid":280341,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:08:34.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"88948b170d3e0982eb59e30349af65a2d2735aa5","tid":1385532,"uid":280341,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:09:23.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"36922ccb2ce78dbd888dd86b8f572efa0f04015e","tid":1385532,"uid":280341,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:09:36.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6996479065a9faadfe572272591ec599024be9e7","tid":1385532,"uid":190630,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:14:05.000Z","msg":"良心都重要 只不過已經有太多證據比大眾判斷 再多盞傷自己 認同經濟角度出發 而阻鐵後首要行動為罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以要大力推"},{"pid":"07a5a0e05fcdcf9aa9c8db6b91a29fb6c7f5ce1e","tid":1385532,"uid":280341,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6996479065a9faadfe572272591ec599024be9e7","tid":1385532,"uid":190630,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:14:05.000Z","msg":"良心都重要 只不過已經有太多證據比大眾判斷 再多盞傷自己 認同經濟角度出發 而阻鐵後首要行動為罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以要大力推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:01:01.000Z","msg":"對我地對市民重要 但係對政府做唔成壓力 佢哋毫不在乎"},{"pid":"eba80aa48f90b49fb09d6aa4ec1f3fa2432ec665","tid":1385532,"uid":208452,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:01:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我剩係知政府咁驚搞的就焗到佢搞就岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日(7月30)1500-2000</span></span>會有義工係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">旺角東天橋</span></span>擺街站等無上連登的市民都可以寫底感受比我地,希望大家支持<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">餓住的小朋友入一入黎, 有心幫佢地都可以黎睇下</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1382980/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1382980/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【眾籌】 已集合超過1000名巴絲感想 香港編年史</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1</a><br />\nTG:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkrevolutiondocument\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkrevolutiondocument&d=BNsYvnDu2JTLJ%2Bl7stKmI9g1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=bfaf67a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkrevolutiondocument</a><br />\nFB:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E4%B9%8B%E6%9B%B8-100576917956000/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2594%25B1%25E4%25B9%258B%25E6%259B%25B8-100576917956000%2F&d=BNsYvnDu2JTLJ%2Bl7stKmI9g1hcd%2FKl8Hg